data.description: Make this beautiful CareFree Hyland resale yours! This home has plenty of living space. Fits 3 cars in garage! Astounding formal living and dinning area as soon as you walk in. Amazing large kitchen with white countertops, gorgeous backsplash and plety of cabinets. Kitchen island, large pantry and a bar. Kitchen opens to the great room offering a lot of space for the holiday family gatherings. Upstairs you have a loft and the laudry room. Three good size bedrooms, huge master with a sitting area to the side. Conveniently close to the outlet mall, I-10 and Transmountain. Backyard is nice and private. Solar panels at NO COST to new buyers! Schedule a showing today!
